Name: Jo-Jo Fighter
About the game: Jo-Jo Fighter is a 2D side-scrolling platformer. You are a loner fighter who was thrown into the jungle. Defeat pirates, smugglers and bandits, get out of the dangerous jungle alive! Features of the game: -The character has a variety of weapons: from a pistol to a grenade launcher -Enemies are armed with different weapons -The appearance and weapons of enemies are randomly generated.
